  "title": "Assistant Warehouse Supervisor #77161",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing/Food Production</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Warehouse Assistant/ Senior Warehouse Assistant</strong></li><li>Working Location: Jurong West</li><li>Working Hours: 5 days, Mon - Fri (8.00am -5.00pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic + $90 (Transport Allowance) + OT + Variable Bonus</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee daily warehouse operations and staff management.</li><li>Coordinate with various departments such as Purchasing, QC/QA, and Production.</li><li>Manage loading, unloading, and storage of materials.</li><li>Keep accurate inventory records in the ERP system and maintain warehouse organization.</li><li>Ensure compliance with safety, quality, and operational standards.</li><li>Support other departments as needed and handle additional tasks assigned by superiors.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Skilled in using MS Office and ERP systems.</li><li>Must have a valid forklift license and be able to operate related equipment (eg stacker).</li><li>Ability to work overtime when needed.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#77161 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
